- Now?
- Yes.

49:40.645 --> 49:42.729
l'll just be a minute.

49:49.695 --> 49:52.989
- Are you comfortable here?
- Yeah, very much, thank you.

49:53.157 --> 49:54.824
Yeah.

50:02.792 --> 50:06.294
So, uh... it was Obote's men
who attacked the prison, yeah?

50:06.462 --> 50:08.338
- Yes.
- Right.

50:08.506 --> 50:12.842
We heard the gunfire
all the way at the hospital.

50:13.010 --> 50:18.973
- Yes. My soldiers, they held them off.
- We thought there'd be lots of casualties.

50:19.141 --> 50:23.978
Do you want to drive your car? I want
to see you drive your car. Please. Come.

50:24.146 --> 50:26.064
- Come.
- OK.

50:36.283 --> 50:40.787
So... you do not like the way I treat my son.

50:42.206 --> 50:44.916
Uh, no. No, I don't.

50:46.252 --> 50:49.212
Hiding him away like that, it's ruining his life.

50:49.380 --> 50:54.634
- That boy has everything he wants.
- Except the treatment that could save him.

50:54.802 --> 50:57.470
He has comfort, a luxury life.

50:57.638 --> 51:00.974
Money, sir, is no substitute for anything.

51:01.142 --> 51:04.978
Nicholas, you have never been poor.

51:06.439 --> 51:08.481
What about Kay? Don't you think...?

51:08.649 --> 51:12.777
Do not speak about things
you do not understand.

51:16.240 --> 51:20.827
But the way you are concerned,
it has touched me

51:20.995 --> 51:23.830
and I will consider.

51:23.998 --> 51:28.168
You know, I like this type
of frank conversation.

51:28.335 --> 51:33.047
Yes, I respect your honesty
and your opinion completely.

51:41.515 --> 51:43.600
Drive! Drive.

51:48.564 --> 51:50.231
Drive past! Drive!

51:54.653 --> 51:56.070
Drive!

52:15.132 --> 52:18.051
Obote's men! l'm sure of it!

52:18.803 --> 52:21.846
lf I had not been in your car...

52:23.140 --> 52:26.643
lt is in my dream. They cannot kill me.

52:26.811 --> 52:28.853
lt is in my dream.

52:34.318 --> 52:37.737
Somebody told his men my travel plans.

52:39.114 --> 52:41.658
Somebody has betrayed me.

52:42.576 --> 52:45.411
l cannot trust anybody.

52:46.539 --> 52:49.123
l'm surrounded by traitors!

52:58.050 --> 53:00.593
Masanga.

53:01.470 --> 53:03.721
Nicholas. Nicholas.

53:04.265 --> 53:06.474
- You know Masanga.
- Uh-huh.

53:06.642 --> 53:08.935
He is one of my people.

53:09.103 --> 53:13.189
He will handle
all of my security matters from now on.

53:13.357 --> 53:14.816
Yes, sir.

53:14.984 --> 53:20.071
- You will take care of me and this country.
- Yes, sir.

53:22.408 --> 53:24.534
Where is Jonah Wasswa?!

53:24.702 --> 53:28.413
Where is he? I need my minister.

53:28.581 --> 53:33.543
A minister should be by his president's side.

53:33.711 --> 53:36.462
- Where is he?!
- I don't know.

53:37.506 --> 53:42.468
And you call yourself my closest adviser.

53:44.388 --> 53:46.347
Huh?

53:53.981 --> 54:00.320
You see? You see? These loyal soldiers,
already they have captured the criminals.

54:26.138 --> 54:28.848
Do not pity them, Nicholas.

54:29.016 --> 54:33.102
These men here, they wanted you dead.

54:35.981 --> 54:39.233
Why did you try to kill me?

54:39.401 --> 54:41.027
Huh?

54:42.196 --> 54:46.449
l will not die until I say.

54:49.495 --> 54:52.997
Look at me.

55:00.506 --> 55:02.590
Huh?

55:02.758 --> 55:06.010
You work for him! Obote!

55:06.178 --> 55:07.261
Huh?!

55:07.429 --> 55:11.641
That... that... drunk, silly man!

55:11.809 --> 55:16.145
You want to kill me for that drunk, silly man?!

55:16.313 --> 55:18.147
Huh?!

55:23.278 --> 55:25.571
Uganda loves me...

55:26.991 --> 55:29.784
because I am loyal...

55:30.828 --> 55:33.705
and I am fair.

55:37.167 --> 55:40.837
l am your president.

55:50.014 --> 55:54.350
Come, Nicholas. This is no place for us.

